Dynegy Coal Trading & Transportation, L.L.C.: Private Company Information - Bloomberg










































  





















































































July 28, 2017 10:15 AM ET
Trading Companies and Distributors

Company Overview of Dynegy Coal Trading & Transportation, L.L.C.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Dynegy Coal Trading & Transportation, L.L.C. distributes coal and coal products. It uses software such as Right Angle System of SolArc Inc. to manage bulk trading and and power station supply operations. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is headquartered in Wilmington, Delaware. Dynegy Coal Trading & Transportation, L.L.C. operates as a subsidiary of Dynegy Inc.


1209 Orange StreetWilmington, DE 19801United StatesFounded in 2000










