About
Dynegy Coal Trading & Transportation Llc is located at the address 1000 Louisiana St in Houston, Texas 77002.  They can be contacted via phone at (713) 507-6400 for pricing, hours and directions.  Dynegy Coal Trading & Transportation Llc has an annual sales volume of 1M – 1,999,999.  .For more information contact West  Boettger, Senior Director or  go to www.dynegy.comFor maps and directions to Dynegy Coal Trading & Transportation Llc view the map to the right.  For reviews of Dynegy Coal Trading & Transportation Llc see below.









